  m_text: "Welcome to Endless Mode!\nIf you don\u2019t know Tic-Tac-Toe rules, play
    Easy & Normal first.\nHere, time is irrelevant\u2014your only goal is the highest
    Win Streak.\nEach round has 3 phases:\nShop \u2192 Battle \u2192 Results\nBuy
    and use items in the Shop.\nVictory rewards coins based on remaining steps, and
    raises next round\u2019s difficulty.\nDraws don\u2019t affect difficulty; losses
    neither, but cost 1 chance.\nYou have 3 chances total.\nGood luck!"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
